{"tid":337004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國斬VPN通殺 傳法國駐華大使館也被斷了","createTime":"2017-07-27T02:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T10:06:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f02a7815709231bf3e36732039f710b02a1b98e","tid":337004,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpDzHrZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpDzHrZD.jpg&h=d8c1b215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國網友當時在微博上議論此事，如今該篇貼文已被刪除。（圖擷自靠北共產黨臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpMOE1AR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpMOE1AR.jpg&h=f986ec4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在頁庫存檔能找回被刪除的相關貼文。（圖擷自微博）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國網路審查嚴格，民眾要瀏覽國外網站，往往需要靠VPN翻牆，不過北京當局最近嚴格管理VPN，昨日傳出甚至連法國駐華大使館的VPN也被斬了，無法連接回法國的數據庫，導致許多人到了使館卻無法辦理簽證。<br />\n<br />\n有中國網友昨日下午在微博上指出，法國大使館的VPN疑似被「牆了」（意指被屏蔽），不少在現場要辦簽證的民眾急得像熱鍋上的螞蟻。還有網友透露，由於連不回法國國內做審核，所以待辦的簽證數量大量累積。<br />\n<br />\n雖然相關微博貼文，於今日已被刪除，但從頁庫存檔仍能找到蛛絲馬跡，證實確曾有中國網友在討論此事。PTT的鄉民在得知此事後，則紛紛感嘆，「習包子全面鎖國，連大使館都不放過」、還有人笑稱，「以後在中國用飛鴿傳書好了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2144303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2144303&d=JLAdynOSApH72bnt5W8YUF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a44bf9de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2144303&h=79d1d18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2144303</a>"},{"pid":"1a4c9dcffe120511558373156edcdd648818630f","tid":337004,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5317